parameters:
\n<Deorc>"Monsters, listen well! This time for sure, we'll crush
Annabern!"

\n<Deorc>"Damn it, could it be that guy tricked me!? Saying Roselitte
isn't here... Damn it!!"
Deorc took out a "book" from his bosom.

\n<Deorc>"Return, my monsters! First, let's take down these
bastards!"

\n<Roselitte>"Ameria! Lyric! If those monsters from before return, we
stand no chance of winning!"

\n<Roselitte>"--Throw all your power at him! Let's settle this once and
for all!!"
\n<Ameria>"Yeah! Leave the support to me, Roselitte-san!"
\n<Lyric>"Charge, Roselitte! We'll scatter any enemies in your way!"
